# Place your product images here:
#
#   hero-capacitor.png  — Full product shot for hero section (right side)
#   can-product.png     — Can image for Product Spotlight section
#   logo-white.png      — White logo for dark backgrounds (Navbar, Footer)
#   logo-black.png      — Black logo for light backgrounds (unused currently)
#
# Recommended sizes:
#   hero-capacitor.png  → at least 800x1200px, PNG with transparent background
#   can-product.png     → at least 600x900px, PNG with transparent background
#   logo-white.png      → at least 200x200px, SVG or PNG, transparent background
